        public void setBoxStart(GeoPoint boxStart)
        Set the start of the region of this request
        Parameters:
        boxStart - The start of the region in which to get data. Northern latitudes are positive and southern latitudes are negative. Eastern hemisphere longitudes are positive and western hemisphere longitudes are negative. Longitudes in North America are negative. The latitude and longitude values are expressed using the WGS 84 datum.
